JP morgan 3rd of tech discussion -

Can you briefly introduce yourself and highlight your key experience in DevOps?

What types of issues have you handled through JIRA? Can you explain one major issue and one minor issue in detail, including your approach and resolution?

If a pod with pod-affinity configured keeps crashing in production, how would you troubleshoot and bring it back online quickly while ensuring traffic is routed to it?

If data is flowing between multiple pods and you need to trace the flow to identify where an issue is occurring, what approaches or tools would you use?

How would you restore a Kubernetes cluster from an etcd backup? Do you know how etcd stores cluster metadata?

Can you explain the overall architecture of Kubernetes and the responsibilities of each component?

Can you collect logs and traces from a Java application? What tools or stack would you use to implement this?

Are you open to working in rotational shifts if required in this role?

How well do you handle high-pressure situations? Can you share an example of a stressful incident you managed and how you approached it?

How does Argo CD deploy manifests to different environments? Can you explain the setup you implemented?

If a production outage occurs, what would be your immediate approach to troubleshoot and resolve the issue as quickly as possible?

